  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Collect Rainwater for 700 Students in Uganda</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Bishop Comboni College Kambuga has experienced a severe water shortage due to the increased population near the campus taking more and more water from the watershed.  The school students and staff spend an extraordinary amount of time fetching water for the myriad uses of the 700 students, plus teachers and staff.  The collection of rainwater at the boys&apos; dorm during the rainy season is a way to alleviate this shortage and provide better quality water to the campus.</narrative>
  </description>
